  "description": {
    "zh": "人们总是在寻找特殊的物品。特别是像你这样的PMC雇佣兵们，那些与本地商人合作密切的人。\n\n一个叫 \"Fence\" 的人总是给大家出同样的挑战。你看，世界各地有很多与知名人物相关的纪念品，而人们的任务就是找到其中的每一种收藏品。\n\n如果你对那些专门为储存这些纪念品而设计的新容器箱子感兴趣，带给我三件这样的收藏品，不用担心重复的，带来就行了，我们可以卖给你更多你需要的箱子。",
    "en": "People are on the hunt for special goods. Specifically people like you, PMCs, people who work with the local vendors a lot.\n\nSomeone called \"Fence\" always gave people the same challenge. You see, there are a ton of these souvenirs related to well known people around the globe and people have the task to find them all, one of each collectible.\n\nIf you are interested in having access to one of these new storage containers which are specifically made to keep these souvenirs, bring me three of these collectibles, don't worry about duplicates, just bring them and we can sell you as many as you need."
  },
